con:request.name: Create test script
con:request.con:request:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:ws="http://ws.api.meveo.org/">\r
   <soapenv:Header/>\r
   <soapenv:Body>\r
      <ws:createOrUpdate>
         	<createOrUpdateScriptInstanceRequest>
            <type>JAVA</type>
            <script>
            <![CDATA[
import java.math.BigDecimal;
import java.util.Map;
import java.util.HashMap;

import org.meveo.admin.exception.BusinessException;
import org.meveo.admin.exception.ValidationException;
import org.meveo.model.shared.DateUtils;
import org.meveo.service.custom.CustomTableService;
import org.meveo.service.script.Script;
import org.apache.commons.collections4.MapUtils;

public class CustomTables${#Project#entityPrefix}_${#TestSuite#index}TestScript extends Script {

    CustomTableService customTableService;

    @Override
    public void init(Map<String, Object> methodContext) throws BusinessException {
        super.init(methodContext);

        customTableService = (CustomTableService) getServiceInterface("CustomTableService");
    }

    @Override
    public void execute(Map<String, Object> methodContext) throws BusinessException {

        Map<String,Object> queryValues = new HashMap<>();
        queryValues.put( "closestMatch prefix", "123456789999887" );
        String zone = (String) customTableService.getValue("${#Project#entityPrefix}_${#TestSuite#index}_ct_zoning", "zone", queryValues);

        if (!"Australia".equals(zone)) {
            throw new ValidationException("Expected zone Australia received " + zone);
        }

        queryValues = MapUtils.putAll(new HashMap<String, Object>(), new Object[]{ "closestMatch prefix", "123456789999887" });

        zone = (String) customTableService.getValue("${#Project#entityPrefix}_${#TestSuite#index}_ct_zoning", "zone", DateUtils.parseDateWithPattern("2016-03-05", DateUtils.DATE_PATTERN), queryValues);

        if (!"Australia West".equals(zone)) {
            throw new ValidationException("Expected zone Australia West received " + zone);
        }

        queryValues = MapUtils.putAll(new HashMap<String, Object>(), new Object[]{"minmaxRange hour_from hour_to", 15, "fromRange price", new BigDecimal(0.6), "toRange price", new BigDecimal(1.2)} );

        Map<String, Object> values = customTableService.getValues("${#Project#entityPrefix}_${#TestSuite#index}_ct_zoning", null, queryValues);

        if (values == null || !"123".equals(values.get("prefix"))) {
            throw new ValidationException("Expected prefix 123 received " + values.get("prefix"));
        }

        queryValues = MapUtils.putAll(new HashMap<String, Object>(), new Object[]{"minmaxRange hour_from hour_to", 15, "fromRange price", new BigDecimal(0.6), "toRange price", new BigDecimal(2)} );

        values = customTableService.getValues("${#Project#entityPrefix}_${#TestSuite#index}_ct_zoning", null, DateUtils.parseDateWithPattern("2018-05-09", DateUtils.DATE_PATTERN), queryValues);

        if (values == null || !"123887".equals(values.get("prefix"))) {
            throw new ValidationException("Expected prefix 123887 received " + values.get("prefix"));
        }

    }
}
		   ]]>
            </script>
         </createOrUpdateScriptInstanceRequest>
      </ws:createOrUpdate>\r
   </soapenv:Body>\r
</soapenv:Envelope>
